name: Mass mortality events in Mediterranean marine coastal ecosystems
description: The Mass Mortality Events database (hereafter MME-T-MEDNet) is a collaborativeinitiative involving more than 30 research institutions from 10 Mediterraneancountriesincluding EU and non-EUcountries. This initiative aims to facilitate the access to information (published in scientific journals and gray literature or still unpublished) related to Mediterranean Mass Mortality Events (MMEs).
